'''Intergalactic Joke Group''' was a service that [[e-mail]]ed a daily joke to its members. [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen]] was probably a subscriber. One of the jokes they sent regarded an [[Angrallian Toobir]].<ref name="XWA" />

